(1, 1, 'The Role of Google Cloud Platform in the Digital World', 'what-is-google-cloud-platform', 'In the modern digital era, cloud computing has become a big deal, and one of the big names in this game is Google Cloud Platform (GCP). It offers cloud computing services like computing, storage, AI, machine learning, and more. What\'s remarkable is that GCP uses the same robust technology that powers Google Search, Gmail, and YouTube.', 'GCP is notable for its powerful data analytics and Machine Learning (ML) features. With tools like BigQuery and AutoML, businesses can innovate and expand quickly and gain a competitive edge in this evolving digital world. But what impact does this have on business, and why should one know about GCP? This article explores the tangible benefits of GCP and its increasing importance in the technology and business sectors.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/browsenest/1_SLn9wrb2R.jpg?updatedAt=1713533120087', 2, 'Google Cloud Platform: A Game Changer in Technology', 'Discover why Google Cloud Platform is the best in cloud computing and how it can help your business grow and improve its operations.', 'Google Cloud Platform, what is Google Cloud platform', 8, '2024-02-22', '2024-10-22 08:17:21'),
(2, 1, 'Data Security Tools and Practices for Online Safety', 'data-security-tools-and-practices', 'In the modern digital world, grasping the complexities of data security has become essential. While the internet offers immense benefits, it also poses risks to your valuable data. Consequently, individuals and businesses must employ practical tools and practices to safeguard their information.', 'This exhaustive guide aims to highlight the importance of data security, describe the concept itself, and present a range of tools and practices to fortify your digital defenses. By the end of this read, you can effectively protect your online assets with the necessary data security knowledge.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/browsenest/2_lP6hxxIYy.jpg?updatedAt=1713533120098', 3, 'Know Everything About Data Security Tools and Practices', 'This detailed data security guide highlights the crucial tools and top practices for protecting your data against cyber threats and breaches.', 'data security, what is data security, data security tools, data security practices', 3, '2024-02-23', '2024-10-22 08:17:21'),
(3, 2, 'Top 5 Business Management Degree Programs Available in India', '5-best-business-management-degree-programs', 'India has undergone a significant economic boom in the past few decades, leading to a rising demand for skilled business experts. As a result, various academic establishments have emerged, offering specialized business management degree programs to meet this growing need.', 'Discover premier business management degree programs in India that empower young individuals with vital knowledge and skills to excel in the dynamic business arena. Both students and employers highly value these sought-after programs.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/browsenest/3_GVXJcKT6S.jpg?updatedAt=1713533120136', 3, '5 Most Popular Business Management Degree Programs in India', '5 best business management degree programs in India for 2024. 1. Indian Institute of Management (IIM) • 2. Indian School of Business (ISB), and more.', 'Business Management Degree, business management degree programs, IIM', 7, '2024-02-24', '2024-10-22 08:17:21'),
(4, 2, 'Essential Digital Marketing Courses for Beginners in 2024', 'digital-marketing-courses-for-beginners', 'Are you considering changing jobs or looking to improve your tech skills? If yes, digital marketing could be a good option. It\'s a field that\'s getting bigger and offers plenty of learning opportunities.', 'However, with so many online digital marketing courses, finding the best one can take a lot of time. This guide explains digital marketing and recommends some top courses for beginners in 2024.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/browsenest/4_p4dkM-srW.jpg?updatedAt=1713533120004', 3, 'Digital Marketing Courses 2024: A Beginner\'s Roadmap', 'Ready to kickstart your digital marketing career? Discover the best beginner digital marketing courses for 2024 and begin improving your skills today.', 'digital marketing courses, digital marketing, digital marketing course', 2, '2024-02-25', '2024-10-22 08:17:21'),
